assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Daitobo Co., Ltd. engages in the commercial facility/real estate, healthcare, fashion apparel and uniform, and other related businesses in Japan and internationally. The company develops commercial facilities, such as shopping malls, and apartment and parking lots; rents housing properties; and purchases and sells real estate properties; and manufactures health related products, such as health foods, futon type home medical equipment, bedding products using health materials. In addition, the company offers textile fabric OEM and knit ODM services; value-added and Chinese materials; and wool, cotton, and synthetic fiber uniforms, as well as uniforms for government offices. The company was formerly known as Daito Woolen Spinning & Weaving Co Ltd and changed its name to Daitobo Co., Ltd. in September 2016. Daitobo Co., Ltd. was founded in 1896 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan.
